               <p>I saw the prisoner take the saddle from the door, I ran after him and brought him back, I called to him to put it up again.</p>
               <p>Court. You might as well have prevented him from taking of it. I did not know he would take it till he did.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. A man employed me to carry it, and I told them, and they would not stop him.</p>
